
- Permit the generation of several applications in subdirectories.
- Move the 'orcc_' folder and the 'generate' script to the library directory.
- Add a Makefile to install the library on the system.
- Add debugging and verbose options to the 'generate' script.

- Map several actors on the same processor.
- Compute the precise memory consumption using an LLVM pass.
- Reduce memory consumption of the actors.
